title: Moonbase 3 DivX6
description:
Wikipedia:

Moonbase 3 is a British science fiction television programme that ran for six episodes in 1973.
The European lunar colony, Moonbase 3, has been in existence for 8 years at the time the series starts. With oversight provided by the European Space Assembly and the European Aeronautics and Space Administration, Moonbase 3 is a shoestring operation when compared with the Russian and American efforts and much of base director David Caulder's job is to stave off budget cuts or a complete shutdown in the face of skeptical bureaucrats.
Alongside technical problems such as stranded astronauts, explosive decompressions and failed experiments, the inhabitants of the moonbase must also deal with psychological problems arising from the cramped, dangerous environment they live in.
